RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.BRANCH_CODE, A.BRANCH_NAME, B.BRANCH_TREASURY_TYPE FROM (SELECT BRANCH_CODE, BRANCH_NAME FROM OLTMS_BRANCH WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' UNION SELECT 'ALL', 'ALL BRANCHES' FROM DUAL WHERE 'ALL' IN (SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM OLTMS_BRN_AF_PRD_MASTER WHERE BRANCH_CODE = 'ALL' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A')) A, OLTMS_BRN_TREAS_PARAMS B WHERE A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE(+)
SELECT CCY_CODE,CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O'
SELECT DISTINCT A.PRODUCT_CODE, A.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT A WHERE A.MODULE = 'OL' AND A.RECORD_STAT ='O' AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY A.PRODUCT_CODE

SELECT A.BRANCH_CODE, A.BRANCH_NAME FROM (SELECT BRANCH_CODE, BRANCH_NAME FROM OLTMS_BRANCH WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' UNION SELECT 'ALL', 'ALL BRANCHES' FROM DUAL WHERE 'ALL' IN (SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM OLTMS_BRN_AF_PRD_MASTER WHERE BRANCH_CODE = 'ALL' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A')) A, OLTMS_BRN_TREAS_PARAMS B WHERE A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE(+)
SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_CODE PRODUCT, PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION PRDDESC FROM OLVWS_AUTO_FUND_MAPPING_PROD

SELECT CUSTOMER_NO,CUSTOMER_NAME FROM(SELECT CUSTOMER_NO, CUSTOMER_NAME1 AS CUSTOMER_NAME FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' UNION ALL SELECT 'ALL' CUSTOMER_NO, 'ALL CUSTOMERS' CUSTOMER_NAME FROM DUAL)
SELECT TREASURY_SOURCE,SOURCE_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_TREASURY_SOURCE WHERE RECORD_STAT= 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND TREASURY_TYPE= NVL(?,'B')
SELECT DEPARTMENT_CODE,DEPARTMENT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_DEPARTMENT WHERE AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O'
